OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776694272
OL,3,CMulti-million pound M27 road works to
OL,4,Cbe lifted after more than two years
OL,6,FMulti-million pound road works that
OL,7,Fhave been in place on part of the M27,
OL,8,Fin Hampshire, for more than two years
OL,9,Fare due to be lifted.
OL,11,FBoth carriageways along the road -
OL,12,Fwhich is a major commuter hub in the
OL,13,Fsouth - will see lane closures between
OL,14,Fjunctions 5 and 7 removed by 6am on
OL,15,FTuesday.
OL,17,FNational Highways said it followed the
OL,18,Fcompletion of its first stage of
OL,19,Ftechnology testing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
