OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1776694272
OL,3,CMulti-million pound M27 road works to
OL,4,Cbe lifted after more than two years
OL,6,FTemporary speed limits of 50mph will,
OL,7,Fhowever, remain in place while the
OL,8,Ffinal stage of testing is carried out.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FThe road works have been in place
OL,16,Fsince February 2024 and cost an
OL,17,Festimated #83 million.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
